{"description": "Building a modern web (or mobile) application requires a lot of tools, frameworks and techniques. This session shows how JHipster unites popular frameworks like AngularJS, Spring Boot and Bootstrap. Using Yeoman, a scaffolding tool for modern webapps, JHipster will generate a project for you and allow you to use Java 7 or 8, SQL or NoSQL databases, Spring profiles, Maven or Gradle, Grunt or Gulp.js, WebSockets and Browsersync. It also supports a number of different authentication mechanisms: classic session-based auth, OAuth 2.0, or token-based authentication. For cloud deployments, JHipster includes out-of-the-box support for Cloud Foundry, Heroku and Openshift.", "event": {"name": "Devoxx UK 2016", "nickname": "devoxx-uk-2016", "twitter": "DevoxxUK", "url": "http://www.devoxx.co.uk/"}, "favorite": "0", "file_date": "2016-12-03", "filename": "get-hip-with-jhipster-spring-boot-angularjs-bootstrap-by-matt-raible", "length": "48:09", "likes": "5", "recorded": "2016-06-08", "short_description": "Building a modern web (or mobile) application requires a lot of tools, frameworks and techniques. This session shows how JHipste", "speaker_twitters": " @mraible", "speakers": {"matt-raible": {"episodes": [], "hosting": [], "info": {"country": "Denver, CO, USA", "github": "mraible", "home": "http://raibledesigns.com/", "name": "Matt Raible", "twitter": "mraible"}, "videos": [{"event": {"name": "Devoxx France 2016", "nickname": "devoxx-france-2016", "twitter": "DevoxxFR", "url": "http://www.devoxx.fr/"}, "filename": "get-hip-with-jhipster-spring-boot-angularjs-bootstrap-matt-raible", "recorded": "2016-04-20", "thumbnail_url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/kkHN2G_nXV0/hqdefault.jpg", "title": "Get Hip with JHipster: Spring Boot + AngularJS + Bootstrap"}, {"event": {"name": "Devoxx France 2016", "nickname": "devoxx-france-2016", "twitter": "DevoxxFR", "url": "http://www.devoxx.fr/"}, "filename": "the-art-of-angular-in-2016-matt-raible", "recorded": "2016-04-20", "thumbn